    "body": "close https://github.com/KMiri-rs/KMiri/issues/83\r\n\r\nStack range of a new task is `0xffffdffffff7e000..0xffffdfffffffe000`, while the vaddr is linear computed via paddr, causing the out-of-bound UB. \r\n\r\nSo a hot fix is saving the non-linear mapping from paddr to vaddr, and the correct vaddr is used in page_walk.",
    "created_at": "2026-07-03T07:47:35Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-07-03T07:51:59Z",
